name: Space Dawg
description: Space Dawg’s sticky buds are known for their delicious flavor and potent indica punch that will have pain (and maybe mental focus) gone in no time. THC levels in this strain have tested at 18-19%, so it might take users on a trip that’s better reserved for night time. TGA Subcool Seeds created this strain by breeding Super Snow Dog with Space Queen. These plants are resilient growers and usually flower within 8 weeks. Space Dawg has a strong skunky smell that is toned down with grapey bubble gum notes. The flavor is just like fruit candy with the right amount of lemony sourness.

highlightedReviews.text: Space Dawg was a strain I picked up because my Bud-tender recommended it to me. I asked for something that would put me to sleep and reduce pain and that's exactly what it did. The smell is very strong. The kind of bud that as soon as you open the jar the room reaks. Fuelly smell with a sweet taste. Had me really spacey for about 30 minutes as I finished up the movie I had been watching than it put me right to sleep. It actually kept me asleep for most of the night (which is rare for me). Overall I would say it's not a bad strain. Definitely good for Insomnia and Stress. 8.5/10

Aha check it nice very smooth smoke plenty of course followed by all of a sudden i realize that i am a big dog in a space suit on my hind legs waiting to be deployed somewhere in outer space. Then the helmet's face sheild came down really smooth and from there i am in a kennel with all these dawgs in a space suits...#Connoisseur.
